===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛə(r)nəs|-ɛə(r)nəs]]

===Noun===
#The state or level of [[consciousness]] where sense data can be confirmed by an [[observer]].
#(Advertising) a key measure used to determine whether or not an advertisement increased consumer knowledge of a company, product, or service, in advertising research.
#: ''[[continuous advertising tracking|Tracking research]] results showed that after the advertising campaign aired, '''awareness''' of iPods increased to 75% of college students as compared to 13% before.''

